      "side": 1,
      "message": "Before my change a few days ago the fast path required the pixelConfig was either RGBA_8888 or BGRA_8888. Technically this was basically checking that the format and colorType combination were of RGBA/BGRA_8888. But I recently made a change to have to just check the colorType because in the world at that time a colorType of RGBA/BGRA_8888 was only supported with a format of RGBA/BGRA_8888. Now with this change a colorType of RGBA_8888 could also be used with  the new compressed format.",
